\c 14 Amazia mambo waJudha 1 Negore rechipiri raJoashi mwanakomana waJoahazi mambo weIsiraeri, Amazia mwanakomana waJoashi mambo waJudha, akatanga kubata ushe. 2 Akatanga kubata ushe ana makore makumi maviri namashanu; akabata ushe paJerusaremu makore makumi maviri namapfumbamwe; zita ramai vake rakanga riri Jehoadhini weJerusaremu. 3 Akaita zvakarurama pamberi paJehovha, asi haana kufanana nababa vake Dhavhidhi; akaita zvose zvakaita baba vake Joashi. 4 Asi matunhu akakwirira haana kubviswa, asi vanhu vakaramba vachibayira nokupisa zvinonhuwira pamatunhu akakwirira. 5 Zvino ushe hwakati huchangosimbiswa naye, akauraya varanda vake vakanga vauraya mambo baba vake. 6 Asi haana kuuraya vana vavaurayi, sezvazvakanyorwa mubhuku yomurayiro waMosesi, sezvakaraira Jehovha, achiti, "Madzibaba ngaarege kuurawa nokuda kwavana, kana vana ngavarege kuurawa nokuda kwamadzibaba; asi munhu mumwe nomumwe ngaafire zvivi zvake." 7 Akauraya vane zviuru zvine gumi zvavaEdhomu pamupata womunyu, akakundawo Sera pakurwa, akaritumidza zita rinonzi Joketeeri, kusvikira zuva ranhasi. 8 Zvino Amazia akatuma nhume kuna Jehoashi mwanakomana waJehoahazi mwanakomana waJehu, mambo weIsiraeri, akati, "Uya tionane." 9 Jehoashi mambo weIsiraeri akatuma shoko kuna Amazia mambo waJudha, akati, "Rukato rwakanga ruri paRebhanoni rwakatuma shoko kumusidhari wakanga uri paRebhanoni, rukati, `Ipa mwanakomana wangu mukunda wako, ave mukadzi wake;' zvino imwe mhuka yakanga iri paRebhanoni ikapfuurapo, ikatsika-tsika rukato. 10 Iwe wakunda vaEdhomu, zvino m.woyo wako wozvikudza; chikudza hako, ugare kumusha; nokuti unotsvakireiko njodzi, uwiremo, iwe naJudha pamwechete newe?" 11 Asi Amazia wakaramba kunzwa. Naizvozvo Jehoashi mambo weIsiraeri
